ey|Edith Varney}}\n|[[Playhouse Theatre]]\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"| <ref>{{cite news|last=Barnes|first=Clive|title=Stage View;'Secret Service' Returns|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9904E1DD143BE43ABC4B52DFB266838D669EDE|work=The New York Times|date=April 13, 1976|accessdate=May 5, 2015|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505101523/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9904E1DD143BE43ABC4B52DFB266838D669EDE|archivedate=May 5, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|1976\n!scope=row|''[[Henry V (play)|Henry V]]''\n| Katherine\n|[[Delacorte Theater]]\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"| <ref name=off>{{cite web|url=http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=people&first=Meryl&last=Streep&middle=|title=Meryl Streep|publisher=[[Lortel Archives]]|accessdate=April 4, 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518224638/http://www.lortel.org/LLA_archive/index.cfm?search_by=people&first=Meryl&middle=&last=Streep|archivedate=May 18, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=show&id=2928|title=Henry V|publisher=Lortel|accessdate=April 4, 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150410215814/http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=show&id=2928|archivedate=April 10, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|1976\n!scope=row|''[[Measure for Measure]]''\n| Isabella\n|[[Delacorte Theater]]\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"| <ref name=off/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=show&id=2929|title=Measure for Measure|publisher=Lortel Archives|accessdate=April 4, 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150410193821/http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=show&id=2929|archivedate=April 10, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Kerr|first=Walter|title=This 'Measure' Falls Short|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=9A06E4DC143EE334BC4A51DFBE66838D669EDE|work=The New York Times|date=Aug