y=show&id=2784|title=Taken in Marriage|publisher=Lortel Archives|accessdate=April 4, 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150410195505/http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=show&id=2784|archivedate=April 10, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 1980\u201381\n!scope=row|''Alice in Concert''\n| Alice\n|[[The Public Theater|Joseph Papp Public Theater]] & Anspacher Theater\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"| <ref name=off/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=show&id=2537|title=Alice in Concert|publisher=Lortel Archives|accessdate=April 4, 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150410203153/http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=show&id=2537|archivedate=April 10, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|2001\n!scope=row|{{Sort|Seagull|''[[The Seagull]]''}}\n| Arkadina\n| [[Delacorte Theater]]\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"| <ref>{{cite news|last=Winer|first=Linda|title=Top-Flight Cast Makes 'The Seagull' Soar|url=https://articles.latimes.com/2001/aug/13/entertainment/ca-33601|work=Los Angeles Times|date=August 13, 2001|accessdate=May 5, 2015|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221092654/http://articles.latimes.com/2001/aug/13/entertainment/ca-33601|archivedate=February 21, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|2004\n!scope=row|''[[Bridge and Tunnel (play)|Bridge and Tunnel]]''\n|Producer\n|Theatres at 45 Bleecker & Bleecker Street Theatre\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"| <ref name=off/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=show&id=3465|title=Sarah Jones: bridge and tunnel|publisher=Lortel Archives|accessdate=April 4, 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150410193348/http://www.lortel.org/lla_archive/index.cfm?search_by=show&id=3465|archivedate=April 10, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|2006\n!scope=row|''[[Mother Courage and Her Children]]''\n| Mother Courage\n|[[Delacorte Theater]]\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"| <ref>{{cite news|last=Rooney|first=David|title=Review: \u2018Mother Courage and Her Children\u2019|url=https://variety.com/2006/legit/reviews/mother-courage-and-her-children-3-1200514009/|work=Variety|date=August 21, 2006|accessdate=May 5, 2015|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505102727/http://variety.com/2006/legit/reviews/mother-courage-and-her-children-3-1200514009/|archivedate=May 5, 2015}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[List of awards and nominations received by Meryl Streep]]\n{{Portal bar|Film|United States}}\n\n==Footnotes==\n{{notelist}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==Bibliography==\n{{Refbegin|30em}}\n* {{cite book |last=Allen |first=David |title=Performing Chekhov |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=raqGAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA132 |date=January 4, 2002 |publisher=Routledge |isbn=978-1-134-65796-4 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Beck |first=Jerry |title=The Animated Movie Guide |url=https://archive.org/details/animatedmoviegui0000beck |url-access=registration |page=[https://archive.org/details/animatedmoviegui0000beck/page/329 329] |date=October 28, 2005 |publisher=Chicago Review Press |isbn=978-1-56976-222-6 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Bergman |first1=Paul |last2=Asimow |first2=Michael |title=Reel Justice: The Courtroom Goes to the Movies |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=9gC2ZSh5qJQC&pg=PA71 |date=April 1, 2006 |publisher=Andrews McMeel Publishing |isbn=978-0-7407-5460-9 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Bigsby |first=Christopher |title=Remembering Arthur Miller |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UQbZAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA29 |date=March 20, 2014 |publisher=A&C Black |isbn=978-1-4081-5016-0 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Corliss |first=Richard |title=Mom in the Movies: The Iconic Screen Mothers You Love (and a Few You Love to Hate) |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FQPZAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA205 |date=April 8, 2014 |publisher=Simon and Schuster |isbn=978-1-4767-3828-4 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Darren |first=Alison |title=Lesbian Film Guide |ur